<title>To Select Sampling Location</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>To Select Sampling Location</h1>
<ol>
<li>Select a Sampler by clicking on its location map or by selecting it from a list of Sampler locations.</li>
</ol>
<a href="HelpPage.html">Return to Help Page</a>
